Vendor: JDColFashion
Type: Leggings
Price: 39.99

A high-waisted performance legging and smooth seams for a distraction- free fit. The Leggins are made of  suplex fabric which is a smart fabric that meets requirements that until now did not exist,  its technology  is superior and  allows correct oxygenation and regulation of skin temperature, even when the type of activity that is performs is intense and prolonged.

 

CHARACTERISTICS AND ADVANTAGES OF SUPLEX LEGGINS:

  • Can be stretched up to 40 percent without losing shape.
  • Its fibers do not wear out Does not wrinkle Does not fade with washes Doesn't shrink.
  • It dries quickly which allows it to be used overnight in both winter and summer.
  • There is a wide range of colors and combinations Allows perspiration and does not stain as a result of sweat.
  • They are flexible garments with a high level of comfort.
  • There are specific models depending on the sports activity carried out Its softness is superior to cotton.
  • It adapts to all body types and perfectly hides cellulite.
  • Guarantee total freedom in terms of movement and flexibility.
